00:26:38,660 --> 00:26:39,690
是的  先生
Yes, sir.

350
00:26:40,280 --> 00:26:41,900
你盯住他
Well, you keep an eye on him.

351
00:26:47,030 --> 00:26:49,750
我要白宫所有人的邮件和电话记录
I want emails and phone records of everyone in the White House.

352
00:26:50,190 --> 00:26:51,340
包括你的
Including yours.

353
00:26:52,240 --> 00:26:54,250
我的  你真觉得...
Mine? You honestly think--

354
00:26:54,250 --> 00:26:55,420
有什么问题吗
Is there a problem?

355
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:57,290
没有
No.

356
00:26:59,280 --> 00:27:00,190
很好
Good.

357
00:27:05,970 --> 00:27:07,020
真是不幸
It's unfortunate.

358
00:27:07,020 --> 00:27:09,390
邓巴女士  邓巴女士
Ms. Dunbar! Ms. Dunbar? Ms. Dunbar?

359
00:27:07,520 --> 00:27:13,980
{\an8}邓巴对"安德伍德2016"照片做出回应

360
00:27:09,400 --> 00:27:10,410
这样的画面
The imagery...

361
00:27:10,690 --> 00:27:12,700
居然有人靠如此卑劣的手段
That anyone would try to inflame racial discord 

362
00:27:12,710 --> 00:27:14,700
企图煽动种族不和
by doing something so base.

363
00:27:14,840 --> 00:27:17,240
那是不是凯文·安德伍德根本不重要
Whether it's Calvin Underwood isn't the point.

364
00:27:17,240 --> 00:27:20,050
即便是  这一点我们无法确认
If it is, and we have no confirmation on that,

365
00:27:20,050 --> 00:27:22,920
那么是谁挂上去的  为什么要这么做
I mean... Who put this up? And why?

366
00:27:22,790 --> 00:27:27,440
{\an8}邓巴对"安德伍德2016"照片做出回应

367
00:27:23,080 --> 00:27:24,280
谁知道呢
Who knows. 

368
00:27:24,280 --> 00:27:27,480
而且父亲的罪未必是孩子的罪
And the sins of the father aren't necessarily the sins of the son.

369
00:27:27,480 --> 00:27:30,840
但  这令人不安  十分不安
But... it's troubling. Very troubling.

370
00:27:31,720 --> 00:27:35,020
这样的伎俩很可能揭开旧疮疤
Stunts like these have the potential to open old wounds.

371
00:27:35,020 --> 00:27:38,320
我们不能允许那样的事发生  我们得不受其影响
We can't let that happen. We need to rise above it.

372
00:27:38,320 --> 00:27:41,130
要明白  不管你支持谁
Make clear, no matter who you support,

373
00:27:41,130 --> 00:27:43,860
这样的行为是不可容忍的
that this sort of behavior will not be tolerated.

374
00:27:43,860 --> 00:27:46,840
给我接克拉克牧师和吉恩·克兰希
Get me Reverend Clark and Gene Clancy on the phone.

375
00:28:07,780 --> 00:28:10,040
他们要你去大巴那边
Hey, they want you out by the bus.

376
00:28:10,380 --> 00:28:11,370
大巴那边
By the bus?

377
00:28:11,370 --> 00:28:13,220
-你是谁  -抱歉
- Um, who are you? - Sorry.

378
00:28:13,220 --> 00:28:14,860
巴特勒县办公室的马克
Mark from the Butler County office.

379
00:28:14,860 --> 00:28:16,160
他们要辛辛那提的志愿者
They want all the Cincinnati volunteers

380
00:28:16,160 --> 00:28:18,130
去大巴那边集合跟邓巴合影
to gather by the bus for a photo with Dunbar.

381
00:28:18,130 --> 00:28:19,590
珍告诉我我不能离开岗位的
Jenn told me I wasn't supposed to leave--

382
00:28:19,590 --> 00:28:20,820
所以她叫我过来喊你
That's why she sent me.

383
00:28:20,820 --> 00:28:22,550
她不希望你错过合影  去吧
She didn't want you to miss the photo. Go.

384
00:28:22,560 --> 00:28:23,890
大巴那边吗
Out by the bus?

385
00:28:24,140 --> 00:28:25,460
她叫我替你
She told me to cover for you.

386
00:28:26,480 --> 00:28:27,840
好
Okay, um...

387
00:28:27,890 --> 00:28:29,610
有几个人没来
well, there were a couple of no-shows,

388
00:28:29,610 --> 00:28:31,300
其他人都来了
but, you know, otherwise, everyone's here.

389
00:28:31,300 --> 00:28:33,610
-好  谢谢  -太棒了  谢谢
- Okay. Thanks. - Very convenient. Thanks.

390
00:28:33,610 --> 00:28:34,530
快去吧
Enjoy.

391
00:29:11,830 --> 00:29:14,050
我是《克利夫兰老实人报》的戴维·格里姆斯
I'm David Grimes with the Cleveland Plain Dealer.

392
00:29:14,980 --> 00:29:16,040
你的证件呢
Where's your credential?

393
00:29:16,050 --> 00:29:18,680
我蠢得把证件忘在车里了
I was an idiot and left it in the car.

394
00:29:18,680 --> 00:29:21,770
