They recognized me at the check-in desk, though.

395
00:29:22,430 --> 00:29:23,550
我可以带你去等候处
I can direct you to the bullpen,

396
00:29:23,550 --> 00:29:24,960
但是这一区不对媒体开放
but this area is off-limits to the press.

397
