There may be more than one.

430
00:31:17,240 --> 00:31:18,960
先打给密查姆  然后克兰希
Meechum first, then Clancy.

431
00:31:25,070 --> 00:31:26,080
卢卡斯
Lucas?

432
00:31:27,600 --> 00:31:28,800
我们得谈谈
We need to talk.

433
00:31:29,500 --> 00:31:32,330
-我还以为你...  -是的  不过已经出来了
- I thought you were--  - I was. I'm... I'm out now.

434
00:31:32,760 --> 00:31:33,990
这很重要
This is important.

435
00:31:35,380 --> 00:31:38,030
总统先生  您父亲是种族主义者吗
Mr. President, was your father a racist?

436
00:31:45,150 --> 00:31:47,300
您父亲是种族主义者吗
Was your father a racist?

437
00:31:50,740 --> 00:31:52,820
安德伍德太夫人  你母亲还好吗
Mrs. Underwood, is your mother okay?

438
00:31:55,250 --> 00:31:56,660
总统先生
Mr. President!

439
00:32:00,900 --> 00:32:02,580
-蔡斯先生  -你是谁
- Mr. Chase? - Who are you?

440
00:32:02,900 --> 00:32:04,490
特勤局的
United States Secret Service.

441
00:32:04,870 --> 00:32:06,050
我们要的不是你  蔡斯先生
We're not after you, Mr. Chase.

442
00:32:06,050 --> 00:32:07,760
我们是想要指使你这么干的人
We're after whoever put you up to it.

443
00:32:07,760 --> 00:32:08,850
指使我做什么
Put me up to what?

444
00:32:09,360 --> 00:32:10,210
你可以现在回答我
You can answer me here, 

445
00:32:10,210 --> 00:32:12,870
或者我们可以去问哥伦比亚办事处
or we can go to the Columbia field office for questioning.

446
00:32:12,940 --> 00:32:14,350
我不知道你在说什么
I have no idea what you're talking about.

447
00:32:14,350 --> 00:32:15,950
请您跟我来一下  先生
All right, I need you to come with me, sir.

448
00:32:15,950 --> 00:32:18,180
-等等  -请出来  先生
- Now, hold on. - Step outside, sir.

449
00:32:18,990 --> 00:32:20,670
我要找律师
I wanna talk to a lawyer.

450
00:32:21,590 --> 00:32:23,620
4126号需要支援
I need backup at 4126.

451
00:32:23,620 --> 00:32:26,330
-没必要这样吧  -除非你合作
- Come on, that's not necessary. - Not if you cooperate, sir.

452
00:32:28,310 --> 00:32:30,700
跟你说不会惹麻烦吧
If I talk to you, I won't get in trouble?

453
00:32:32,240 --> 00:32:34,580
我向上帝起誓  邓巴女士  这都是真的
I swear to God, Ms. Dunbar. It's all true.

454
00:32:34,580 --> 00:32:35,700
证据呢
Then where's the proof?

455
00:32:35,700 --> 00:32:38,410
我没办法找证据  但你可以
I don't have the means, but you do.

456
00:32:39,060 --> 00:32:41,700
你调查过他  你知道他很危险
You've investigated him before. You know he's dangerous.

457
00:32:41,710 --> 00:32:42,500
古德温先生
Mr. Goodwin--

458
00:32:42,500 --> 00:32:44,740
如果我不是查到了真相  他为什么要针对我
Why would he go after me if I wasn't onto something?

459
00:32:44,740 --> 00:32:47,010
这是一起高级钓鱼执法
This was a high-level sting operation.

460
00:32:47,010 --> 00:32:49,060
还为此调动了大量资源
Major resources were dedicated to it.

461
00:32:49,060 --> 00:32:51,550
我原本是个记者  没有犯罪记录
I'm... I was a journalist, no criminal record.

462
00:32:51,550 --> 00:32:53,330
怎么突然就成了威胁  除非我...
How am I suddenly such a threat, unless I'm--

463
00:32:53,340 --> 00:32:54,700
就算我相信你
Even if I did believe you,

464
00:32:54,700 --> 00:32:58,410
我已经不是司法部的了  现在只是个普通市民
I am no longer part of the DOJ. I am a private citizen now.

465
00:32:58,410 --> 00:32:59,750
正在竞选总统
Who's running for president--

466
00:32:59,750 --> 00:33:02,150
你来这儿不违反证人保护计划的规定吗
Aren't you breaking WITSEC protocol by being here?

467
00:33:02,160 --> 00:33:03,790
我不想再跟他谈了
I am no longer comfortable with this.

468
00:33:03,790 --> 00:33:05,820
你是我最后的机会  求你了
You're... you're my last chance. Please!

469
00:33:05,820 --> 00:33:08,350
-我建议你还是回家吧  -我  可是我
- I suggest that you go back home. - I'm... The things I've--

470
00:33:08,350 --> 00:33:10,580
-别逼我们叫保安  -求你了  就
- Don't make us get security involved.  - Please. Just--

471
00:33:10,580 --> 00:33:13,070
你得在这儿等五分钟  让她离开
Just give us five minutes until she's out of the building.

472
00:33:13,070 --> 00:33:15,800
求你了  求你听我说
Please. Please listen to me.

473
00:33:16,150 --> 00:33:17,580
我求你了
I'm... I'm begging you.

474
00:33:17,900 --> 00:33:19,300
帮帮我
Just help me...

475
00:33:19,900 --> 00:33:20,970
帮帮我
Help.

476
00:33:28,570 --> 00:33:31,230
求你了  求你了
Please, please...

477
00:33:33,350 --> 00:33:34,650
天呐
Oh, God...

478
00:33:36,230 --> 00:33:38,100
你怎么能带他来见我
How could you put me in a room with him?

479
00:33:38,320 --> 00:33:39,980
我并不知道他想要说什么
I didn't know what he was gonna say.

480
00:33:39,980 --> 00:33:41,730
不过我以为他这么煞费苦心
But I assumed that if he went to such great lengths--

481
00:33:41,730 --> 00:33:44,990
他只有酒驾的证据  那什么都不算上
The DUI, that's all he has proof of. That's nothing.

482
00:33:44,990 --> 00:33:47,100
我都帮过别人逃脱酒驾的惩罚
Even I have helped people get off for that.

483
00:33:47,100 --> 00:33:49,540
-还有外遇  -没证据
- There's the affair... - With no evidence.

484
00:33:49,540 --> 00:33:52,240
他又在那扯什么谋杀  还杀了两个
Then he leaps to murder... Two murders?

485
00:33:52,240 --> 00:33:53,720
这人有病
The man is troubled.

486
00:33:53,940 --> 00:33:55,520
他那眼神我们都看见了
We saw the look in his eye.

487
00:33:55,710 --> 00:33:57,990
我以为他有什么真凭实据呢
I thought he might have something real.

488
00:33:58,280 --> 00:34:00,000
他以前做编辑做得挺好的
He used to be a good editor.

489
00:34:00,090 --> 00:34:02,020
可他现在是个定了罪的重犯
And now he is a convicted felon.

490
00:34:02,030 --> 00:34:04,080
你说的要不遗余力
You said no stone unturned.

491
00:34:06,530 --> 00:34:09,300
对不起  我应该想得更周到一些的
I'm sorry, I should have thought better of it.

492
00:34:09,300 --> 00:34:10,640
是啊  你是应该
Yes, you should have.

493
00:34:13,100 --> 00:34:15,920
就这样吧  我们在南卡罗来纳情况如何
Let's let it go. How are we doing in South Carolina?

494
00:34:15,930 --> 00:34:17,430
早期民调结果不错
Early exit polls are good.

495
00:34:17,810 --> 00:34:20,540
-我们有机会赢  -真能赢吗
- We have a shot at winning. - Actually winning?

496
00:34:21,050 --> 00:34:22,810
那个广告牌造成了不小的破坏
That billboard's done real damage.

497
00:34:27,600 --> 00:34:29,120
你能这么做我很感激  吉恩
I appreciate you doing this, Gene. 

498
00:34:29,120 --> 00:34:30,910
你真是救了我一命
You're really saving my life here.

499
00:34:30,910 --> 00:34:33,230
等我竞选县长的时候你记着就行
Just remember it when I run for county executive.

500
00:34:33,230 --> 00:34:35,140
你随时需要我随时过来
I'll be down here whenever you need me.

501
00:34:35,140 --> 00:34:38,530
重点不在时间  而是给什么和给多少
Oh, it's not the when, it's the what. And how much.

502
00:34:41,750 --> 00:34:43,360
下午好  奥林
Afternoon, Oren.

503
00:34:43,590 --> 00:34:45,880
-总统先生  -坐吧
- Mr. President. - Have a seat.

504
00:34:50,090 --> 00:34:53,350
上次大桃子的事儿你还没长记性啊
Didn't you learn your lesson with all that Peachoid nonsense?

505
00:34:54,710 --> 00:34:57,140
你说了要帮我搞定第4选区的
Well, you promised to help me with the 4th.

506
00:35:01,140 --> 00:35:03,470
我被怨恨蒙蔽了
I let my bitterness get the better of me.

507
00:35:06,010 --> 00:35:08,200
谁找的你  一个女的吗
Who specifically approached you? A woman?

508
00:35:08,200 --> 00:35:10,610
-黑头发  -对
- Brunette?  - Yeah.

509
00:35:10,610 --> 00:35:13,800
大概这么高  挺好看的
Uh, about so tall, good-looking.

510
00:35:14,330 --> 00:35:15,960
也不告诉我名字
Wouldn't give me her name.

511
00:35:16,000 --> 00:35:17,170
我们应该把所有的
We should get photos

512
00:35:17,170 --> 00:35:19,840
邓巴团队里符合描述的人的照片找来
of everyone in Dunbar's staff that fits that description.

513
00:35:19,840 --> 00:35:21,290
已经在整理了  夫人
Already compiling it, ma'am.

514
00:35:24,300 --> 00:35:25,450
至于你嘛
And as for you...

515
00:35:26,630 --> 00:35:29,460
你要去上电视  越多越好
you're gonna plant yourself in front of as many TV cameras

516
00:35:29,460 --> 00:35:31,760
愿意拍你的都去上
that can gather around that bony ass of yours.

517
00:35:31,760 --> 00:35:34,570
你要表现出被罪恶感折磨  然后良心发现
You're gonna be wracked with guilt and overcome with conscience.

518
00:35:34,570 --> 00:35:37,490
你做好了  我就确保你不会被起诉
And you do that and I'll make sure that you aren't charged.

519
00:35:38,160 --> 00:35:39,410
你想让我说是邓巴指使的吗
You want me to say it was Dunbar?

520
00:35:39,410 --> 00:35:42,570
拜托  聪明点  奥林  她会告你诽谤的
Come on, be smarter than that, Oren. She'll sue you for slander.

