694
00:47:01,320 --> 00:47:03,840
现在生气也没用
Nothing is going to come from anger right now.

695
00:47:23,080 --> 00:47:26,590
昨晚聊天的时候  你说这座房子是宫殿
Last night when we were talking, you called this house a palace.

696
00:47:27,700 --> 00:47:29,380
这是我们开始的地方
This is where we began.

697
00:47:30,510 --> 00:47:33,120
你还记得我母亲差点离开了爸爸
And do you remember when my mother almost left Daddy

698
00:47:33,120 --> 00:47:35,420
就因为他资助了你的竞选吗
because he funded your campaign?

699
00:47:35,750 --> 00:47:37,680
她就有那么讨厌你
That's how much she hated you.

700
00:47:38,430 --> 00:47:39,660
但我当时不在意
But I didn't care,

701
00:47:39,980 --> 00:47:42,470
因为我看到了你的潜质  我看到了未来
because I saw something. I saw a future.

702
00:47:42,730 --> 00:47:43,820
我们的未来
Our future.

703
00:47:44,420 --> 00:47:47,690
你开始摧毁一切以前  我们本还有未来
We had a future until you started destroying it.

704
00:47:47,850 --> 00:47:49,940
要不你不会听的
Well, you wouldn't have listened otherwise.

705
00:47:49,940 --> 00:47:51,900
我一直都听你的
I always listen to you.

706
00:47:52,450 --> 00:47:54,830
只在我说了你想听的的时候
Only when it's what you want to hear.

707
00:47:55,800 --> 00:47:59,530
好吧  克莱尔  我现在在听
Well, all right, Claire. I'm listening now.

708
00:47:59,720 --> 00:48:02,720
你有什么话这么想说
What is it you so desperately needed to say?

709
00:48:03,290 --> 00:48:05,510
三十年来我们从没输过竞选
We've never lost a race in 30 years.

710
00:48:05,510 --> 00:48:08,420
我们从这里开始  所向披靡
We started here and we've always won.

711
00:48:08,420 --> 00:48:09,810
你我一起
You and I, together.

712
00:48:10,730 --> 00:48:12,720
但你要输了  弗兰西斯
But you are losing, Francis.

713
00:48:13,130 --> 00:48:15,500
人们承受不起高价油
People are getting killed at the gas pumps.

714
00:48:16,260 --> 00:48:18,690
《美国就业法案》不及预期
America Works is falling flat.

715
00:48:19,010 --> 00:48:22,810
你的竞选经理看不清现在的形势
Your campaign manager is ten years behind ten years ago.

716
00:48:23,670 --> 00:48:25,460
你没有可靠的竞选伙伴
You don't have a viable running mate.

717
00:48:25,460 --> 00:48:27,890
我们都清楚不能是唐纳德·布莱斯
We both know it can't be Donald Blythe.

718
00:48:28,030 --> 00:48:29,470
当然不能
Well, of course not.

719
00:48:29,470 --> 00:48:31,400
但我连名都提不上
But I have to win the goddamn nomination 

720
00:48:31,400 --> 00:48:33,980
-还考虑什么输赢  -就算我没这么做
- before I can start worrying about winning. - Even if I hadn't done what I did,

721
00:48:33,980 --> 00:48:36,210
你的竞选也问题重重
your race is in real trouble.

722
00:48:37,220 --> 00:48:38,600
你需要我  弗兰西斯
You need me, Francis.

723
00:48:39,650 --> 00:48:42,050
我的支持率比你高
My approvals are higher than yours.

724
00:48:42,050 --> 00:48:43,750
我能帮你赢下德州
I can help you win Texas.

725
00:48:43,900 --> 00:48:46,940
没错  所以我不希望你在达拉斯竞选
Exactly. Which is why I didn't want you running in Dallas.

726
00:48:46,940 --> 00:48:49,000
我需要你在我身旁
I need you at my side.

727
00:48:49,000 --> 00:48:51,160
没错  但是以另一种方式
Yes, but in a different way.

728
00:48:51,480 --> 00:48:52,660
什么方式
Different how?

729
00:48:53,700 --> 00:48:56,260
我们能相互扶持  让彼此更强  对吧
We make each other stronger, can we agree to that?

730
00:48:57,170 --> 00:48:59,870
那得步调协调  但现在不是这样
When it's working, but it's not working.

731
00:48:59,870 --> 00:49:01,390
我们能协调好
We can make it work.

732
00:49:02,590 --> 00:49:06,990
我们能实现当初结婚时我看到的未来
We can accomplish that future I saw when we first got married.

733
00:49:07,530 --> 00:49:11,110
我们作为伙伴  真正的伙伴
It was us, as partners, real partners.

734
00:49:11,910 --> 00:49:13,830
我们再一起竞选吧
Let's run together, again.

735
00:49:14,270 --> 00:49:16,560
不只作为夫妻
Not just as husband and wife.

736
00:49:24,150 --> 00:49:25,410
你不是指...
You don't mean...

737
00:49:26,030 --> 00:49:26,950
没错
Yes.

738
00:49:30,840 --> 00:49:33,140
我很担心你  克莱尔
I'm worried about you, Claire.

739
00:49:35,200 --> 00:49:38,020
你在说疯话  你被自负蒙蔽了
You're not making any sense. You've let your ego get in the way--

740
00:49:38,020 --> 00:49:39,980
我一直都是你的竞选伙伴
I've always been your running mate.

741
00:49:39,980 --> 00:49:42,720
-你只是不愿承认  -当我的副总统吗
- You just didn't wanna see it. - As my vice president?

742
00:49:42,720 --> 00:49:45,270
-天啊  你知道这...  -我反复考虑过了
- Jesus. Do you have any idea--  - I've put a lot of thought into this.

743
00:49:45,280 --> 00:49:46,750
你肯定没想清楚
You can't have thought it through.

744
00:49:46,750 --> 00:49:48,340
-如果你真想透彻了  -她没经验
- Because if you did, you'd come up - She has no experience. 

745
00:49:48,340 --> 00:49:49,700
-就能想到千万个理由  -她从没竞选过
- with a million reasons-- - She's never run for anything.

746
00:49:49,700 --> 00:49:53,740
无子  任人唯亲  傲慢  我都考虑过了
No children, nepotism, arrogance, I've run through them all.

747
00:49:55,520 --> 00:49:57,270
没我你赢不了
You can't win without me.

748
00:49:59,960 --> 00:50:03,880
我宁愿选懦弱的唐纳德·布莱斯当我副总统
I would rather have a spineless Donald Blythe as my vice president

749
00:50:03,880 --> 00:50:06,900
也强过一个没当选过公职的女人
than a woman who's never held elected office.

750
00:50:07,470 --> 00:50:10,960
你要输给一个没当选过公职的女人了
You're losing to a woman who's never held elected office.

751
00:50:12,460 --> 00:50:14,570
你不配
You don't deserve it.

752
00:50:14,840 --> 00:50:19,170
你没尝过一无所有的滋味
You have no idea what it means to have nothing.

753
00:50:19,170 --> 00:50:22,650
你不重视我们的成就
You don't value what we have achieved.

754
00:50:23,560 --> 00:50:27,650
我这辈子事事都要靠自己努力争取
I have had to fight for everything my entire life.

755
00:50:32,490 --> 00:50:34,270
你知道我为什么留着这张照片吗
Do you know why I kept this?

756
00:50:34,910 --> 00:50:35,980
你知道吗
Do you know?

757
00:50:36,510 --> 00:50:40,540
因为这是我唯一一次为我父亲骄傲
Because it's the one time I was proud of my father.

758
00:50:40,910 --> 00:50:45,260
因为这个男人在这一刻  虽然可鄙
Because this man, in this moment, as despicable as it was,

759
00:50:45,260 --> 00:50:47,520
在为生存而奋斗
is fighting to survive.

760
00:50:48,140 --> 00:50:51,210
他不惜一切
He is doing whatever it took.

761
00:50:51,920 --> 00:50:54,510
有没有你  我也会这样
And so will I, with or without you.

762
00:50:54,510 --> 00:50:57,350
所以我不要跟你谈下去了
So no, I will not have this conversation.

763
00:50:57,350 --> 00:50:59,140
我不会再纵容你了
I will not indulge you any further.

764
00:50:59,140 --> 00:51:00,590
你得放弃
You have to let this go.

765
00:51:01,410 --> 00:51:04,680
我可以参与你的竞选  也可以结束你的竞选
I can be a part of your campaign, or I can end it.

766
00:51:07,170 --> 00:51:10,330
我也会不惜一切  就像你父亲那样
I'll do whatever it takes, too. Just like your father.

767
00:51:11,130 --> 00:51:13,040
但我不会放弃
But I will not let this go.

768
00:51:22,500 --> 00:51:24,920
给我备辆车去格林维尔机场
I'll need a car to the Greenville Airport.

769
00:51:25,780 --> 00:51:27,840
去达拉斯  没错
To Dallas, yes.

